{
  "stem": "9156.9",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And this had an awful lot of meaning to me, that there was this, for Kohler.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There was Hans Litten who was related to that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But I might forget other things that had enormous impact, because you have to remember, there's so many people and so many things after that.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And all the people-- now, I have to say that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That was '50, '51.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then I came back in '54 under the Unitarian Service Committee.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I-- I learned what it meant for people who came out of a concentration camp when they gave them a white piece of paper and said, draw something, they couldn't.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That was terror to look at that white paper.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the one woman ran into the kitchen-- I've never forgotten that-- came out and started all green and red.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "She had seen tomatoes and cucumber.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And thank God, that was the one thing that got her back to be half-normal again.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It was something tangible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But you had to learn that you can't just tell people, draw something.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, there were all kinds of people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were not only survivors.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a Unitarian Service Committee that was working.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I came in occasionally.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I've been back several times.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I have to say, if I start on that, it becomes very difficult, because I give you all that.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But meanwhile, I'm writing so many books, and I-- and friend of mine said, don't even talk about it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This is a matter of public record.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So that's just as well.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that's OK.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I will not talk about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But what it means, that meanwhile, I can do what I believe so strongly in, and that is for-- fight for the dignity of all people everywhere.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
